{"tid":107742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友無心慶祝情人節","createTime":"2017-02-04T16:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T16:53:02.000Z","uid":82383,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eced1382709eea6898f034690689286be4c27e89","tid":107742,"uid":82383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"男朋友好似無乜唸住整啲表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係佢初戀，一齊左四個月，<br />\n平時佢樣樣都好好，<br />\n但佢份人比較無情趣，但話晒第一個情人節，<br />\n想收到少少表示，唔過份呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔係物質主意，<br />\n寫張卡比我，我已經會好開心。<br />\n<br />\n有暗示過，但男朋友表示佢翻工好忙<br />\n放工大陪份時間都係見我，<br />\n一係就好攰，<br />\n無時間預備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係想佢放啲心思係我身上姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 : 大家啱啱grad，啱啱做左嘢無幾耐"},{"pid":"f941638661360df6177605ab7797e73e41a745aa","tid":107742,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"翻工真係好攰 原諒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44afe15b2edf6ae83e3c849be45b3695855ac30d","tid":107742,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"情人節都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dcb4f89a24216d815d65c3673e039d6bfc16e6","tid":107742,"uid":82383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻工真係好攰 原諒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少少表示，買蛋糕都唔過份啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一枝花都好呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5bc0157393152885902c81a6ce8c57614